title: ⛴ "If the goal of a captain was to preserve his ship he would keep it docked forever" - Thomas Aquinas
content:
Given a string S containing only digits, write a function that returns a list containing all possible combinations of valid IPv4 IP addresses.

Example:

$ getIp('11211') 1.1.2.11 1.1.21.1 1.12.1.1 11.2.1.1
